{"tid":130756,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮唔係因為窮，係因為唔識用錢","createTime":"2017-02-22T15:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T18:00:40.000Z","uid":46219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"136ba458786aef767e2256c9a812e719369fd9c6","tid":130756,"uid":46219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"窮唔係因為窮，係因為唔識用錢<br />\n就算俾佢有錢 都唔會有錢淨<br />\n<br />\n由細到大 老豆同阿媽周不時為錢嘈交 <br />\n成日話份糧唔夠洗 而家終於明<br />\n我呀媽好少帶我周圍去街市格價 只會點我去附近買菜<br />\n依家佢買餸 買咗幾百蚊 我都唔知佢買咗啲乜<br />\n原來佢淨係識去李嘉誠超市買嘢 唔怪得俾人搵笨柒<br />\n<br />\n另外就係供樓 完全係搵笨柒之中最戇鳩<br />\n又要自住 又要扮投資 想一雞兩味 肯定發緊夢<br />\n我屋企細個為咗層居屋 成份糧拎哂去供<br />\n搞到我營養不良 返學鞋爛咗 校服唔啱著 都無換<br />\n到依家屋企環境好少少又走去供私樓 仲要供三十年<br />\n即係要仔女幫手埋單 痴撚線 仲話第時都係我地嘅<br />\n（我屋企有幾個仔女 放心係靠唔到父幹）<br />\n三十年後 政府可能唔續契 到時層樓一個仙都唔值<br />\n續契都要俾幾球嘢 累撚死人<br />\n供樓最怕供得長 息口浮動大 供嘅錢唔知幾多去咗利息<br />\n所以一句<span style=\"color: red;\"> 無錢咪撚學人買樓</span><br />\n我無打算俾家用 亦無打算要老豆啲資產<br />\n（因為根本唔值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"e8452ca0af25f93db033c93484c85280cf395088","tid":130756,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ac72f4e8232136ab967b3e6fe6d27af6161083c","tid":130756,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n........................."},{"pid":"e9570741a9e5033473eb34c3fc00ce99b535c6cf","tid":130756,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:30:00.000Z","msg":"十幾年後<br />\n樓主應該喊晒口<br />\n諗點解自己當初咁on9"},{"pid":"c91f919f145615c2aaf25702ed4ef218b598aabb","tid":130756,"uid":58385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"咁似我爸媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過果時冇買私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n03年果時買，而家就發左啦，要我借錢供都濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買多幾間都得<br />\n可惜我果時仲係中學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1c7a47e342f5ddc511f6f358161b2fa43559af","tid":130756,"uid":46219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十幾年後<br />\n樓主應該喊晒口<br />\n諗點解自己當初咁on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十幾年後 我都中年<br />\n搵嘅錢 都夠自己洗<br />\n我唔想孭債上身咁戇鳩"},{"pid":"7dde1e593526ba35dede389c1f2a2076fce65ead","tid":130756,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"唔買<br />\n租?"},{"pid":"ee29441311460c675dc342ddcc74b4907758cc13","tid":130756,"uid":46219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔買<br />\n租?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n租聽落去好似同供樓差唔多錢<br />\n但供樓要孭債 供唔到 負資產就玩完"},{"pid":"554d46d6aa5716cbd399aed1614f6026728c9beb","tid":130756,"uid":58866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:47:02.000Z","msg":"算啦你 諗得呢啲垃圾證明你冇錢<br />\n諗下點發圍好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18eb4ed10119752c4ac8fbc53bbfb41a307fc217","tid":130756,"uid":46219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦你 諗得呢啲垃圾證明你冇錢<br />\n諗下點發圍好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發唔發圍 同 慳錢 係無關係㗎喎<br />\n你無用錢概念 就算俾你中六合彩都係會洗哂<br />\n一年幾多新聞講啲中彩券嘅人破產離婚瞓街 你自己去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dd37055d17deae8f35cf3e00524702bbdc718d","tid":130756,"uid":46219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:00:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁似我爸媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過果時冇買私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n03年果時買，而家就發左啦，要我借錢供都濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買多幾間都得<br />\n可惜我果時仲係中學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個時勢如果唔係full pay買樓 都唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}